                            <p>We utilize traffic log cookies to identify the web pages you visit. This helps us analyze data regarding web page traffic and enhance our website to better fulfil customer requirements. The information collected from cookies is used solely for statistical analysis and is subsequently removed from the system. Overall, cookies assist us in delivering an improved website experience by enabling us to monitor which pages are most valuable to you.</p>
                            <p>Please note that cookies do not grant us access to your computer or any information about you that you have not explicitly shared with us. You have the choice to accept or decline cookies, although most web browsers automatically accept them. However, you can modify your browser settings to decline cookies if you prefer. It is important to be aware that this may restrict your ability to utilize certain features of our website.</p>
